      • SingleRunnerStatistics

        public SingleRunnerStatistics(ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams ps,
                              int n,
                              int v,
                              int c,
                              int managedVMs,
                              long st,
                              long t,
                              long nbN,
                              long nbB,
                              boolean to,
                              long cd,
                              long sd)
        Make new statistics.
        Parameters:
        n - the number of nodes in the model
        v - the number of VMs in the model
        c - the number of constraints
        managedVMs - the number of VMs managed by the algorithm.
        st - the moment the computation starts (epoch format)
        t - the solving duration in milliseconds
        nbN - the number of opened nodes at the moment
        nbB - the number of backtracks at the moment
        to - true to indicate the solver hit a timeout
        cd - the duration of the core-RP building process
        sd - the duration of the core-RP specialization process
